From 57528dc75bf7a74794d460d172280d000bf1f120 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Kol Crooks <kol.crooks@datadoghq.com>
Date: Wed, 6 May 2026 13:44:45 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] Diff body: drop flex-grow, let CSS size to content
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

The empty-space-below-the-card bug wasn't a Monaco measurement issue —
it was layout above Monaco. `.krt-pr-editor-body.diff` had
`flex: 1 1 auto` which stretched the body to the entire pane height
regardless of how tall its content was; same on `.krt-pr-diff`. The
Monaco container inside was correctly sized via getContentHeight, but
the parent ignored it and held the rest of the pane.

Switched both to natural sizing:

- `.krt-pr-editor-body.diff`: `display: block` (no flex-stretch).
- `.krt-pr-diff`: removed `flex: 1 1 auto` and `min-height: 0`.

The root `.krt-pr-editor` is already a vertical flex column with
`overflow: auto`, so a tall file stack scrolls naturally now and a
short stack hugs the bottom of the last card.

Monaco's per-card height is still JS-driven via getContentHeight + the
settling poll — that part is irreducible because Monaco's internals
use absolute positioning. But every layer outside Monaco is now pure
CSS; no flex-grow fighting content.
---
 .../contrib/krt/browser/pr/krtPullRequestEditorPane.css    | 7 ++-----
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 5 deletions(-)

diff --git a/src/vs/workbench/contrib/krt/browser/pr/krtPullRequestEditorPane.css b/src/vs/workbench/contrib/krt/browser/pr/krtPullRequestEditorPane.css
index 7281a428c1c..1aadc901a6c 100644
--- a/src/vs/workbench/contrib/krt/browser/pr/krtPullRequestEditorPane.css
+++ b/src/vs/workbench/contrib/krt/browser/pr/krtPullRequestEditorPane.css
@@ -739,18 +739,15 @@
 
 /* ---------- Diff body ---------- */
 
+/* Diff body + grid: size to content, not flex-fill. The root .krt-pr-editor is a flex column with overflow:auto, so a tall file stack scrolls naturally; flex-grow here would stretch the body to pane height regardless of content. */
 .krt-pr-editor-body.diff {
-	display: flex;
-	flex: 1 1 auto;
-	min-height: 0;
+	display: block;
 }
 
 .krt-pr-diff {
 	display: grid;
 	grid-template-columns: 260px 1fr;
 	gap: 16px;
-	flex: 1 1 auto;
-	min-height: 0;
 	width: 100%;
 }
 
